            { id: 20, type: "numerical", text: "Let {a<sub>n</sub>}<sub>n=1</sub><sup>‚àû</sup> be a sequence such that a<sub>1</sub> = 1, a<sub>2</sub> = 1 and a<sub>n+2</sub> = 2a<sub>n+1</sub> + a<sub>n</sub> for all n ‚â• 1. Then the value of ‚àë<sub>n=1</sub><sup>47</sup> (21a<sub>n</sub>) is equal to", correct: 7 }
